python-ndn
==========

|Test Badge|
|Code Size|
|Release Badge|
|Doc Badge|

A Named Data Networking client library with AsyncIO support in Python 3.

It supports Python >=3.9 and PyPy3.9 >=7.3.8.

Please see our documentation_ if you have any issues.

